data.title: Former NBA champion Metta World Peace (Ron Artest)
data.meta_description: Download Image of Former NBA champion Metta World Peace (Ron Artest). Free for commercial use, no attribution required. Former NBA champion Metta World Peace (Ron Artest) gave a lesson in defense to defenders at March Air Reserve Base, California, appearing at a Los Angeles Lakers military appreciation event September 9, 2018. March ARB is the home of the 452d Air Mobility Wing of the Air Force Reserve Command and the 163d Attack Wing of the California Air National Guard, among other military units. (U.S. Air National Guard photo by Tech. Sgt. [CA] Gregory Solman). Dated: 09.09.2018.
